Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: ffprobe command not found

Solution: Install FFmpeg suite: sudo apt install ffmpeg -y
Issue: Python import errors for ffmpeg or pymediainfo

Solution: Reinstall libraries: pip3 install --upgrade ffmpeg-python pymediainfo
Issue: Permission denied when running scripts

Solution: Make scripts executable: chmod +x script_name.sh or chmod +x script_name.py
Issue: No metadata extracted from video file

Solution: Verify file is valid video format: file video_file.mp4 and check file isn't corrupted
Issue: JSON parsing errors in Python

Solution: Validate JSON output: python3 -m json.tool metadata.json
